\"ph sap-technical-name sap-technical-name\">FTI_TR_POSITIONS</span></p></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"a430c753b1081d4be10000000a174cb4.html\">Issue Volumes</a></p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p><span class=\"ph sap-technical-name sap-technical-name\">CFM_DEAL_02</span></p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p><span class=\"ph sap-technical-name sap-technical-name\">/SAPQUERY/CFM_ISSUE</span></p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p><span class=\"ph sap-technical-name sap-technical-name\">FTI_TR_DEALS</span></p></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"a730c753b1081d4be10000000a174cb4.html\">Issue Charges</a></p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p><span class=\"ph sap-technical-name sap-technical-name\">CFM_DEAL_01</span></p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p><span class=\"ph sap-technical-name sap-technical-name\">/SAPQUERY/CFM_ISSUE</span></p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p><span class=\"ph sap-technical-name sap-technical-name\">FTI_TR_DEALS</span></p></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"aa30c753b1081d4be10000000a174cb4.html\">Issue Hedge</a></p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p><span class=\"ph sap-technical-name sap-technical-name\">CFM_DEAL_03</span></p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p><span class=\"ph sap-technical-name sap-technical-name\">/SAPQUERY/CFM_ISSUE</span></p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p><span class=\"ph sap-technical-name sap-technical-name\">FTI_TR_DEALS</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\"><img class=\"inline\" src=\"loio454470533fe4761ee10000000a174cb4_LowRes.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"> Proceed as follows if you would first like to see an overview of how a certain query\nis <span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">structured</span>:</p>\n<ol class=\"ol\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Use transaction <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">SAP Query: Start Queries</span>\n(<span class=\"ph sap-technical-name sap-technical-name\">SQ00</span>).</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Select one user group and one query.</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Description</span>.</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">This gives you an overview of general information and options for the selected query:</p><ol class=\"ol\" type=\"a\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Query title </p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Author and user to last make changes</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Comments regarding the query</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">InfoSet used to define the query</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Origin of the selected data</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Generated lists (sublists)</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Additional selections</p></li></ol></li></ol>\n</div><div class=\"related-links\"> </div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
